(12821, 1207, 'text', '&nbsp;\r\n<h2><strong>HIGHLY CURATED SELECTION OF NATURAL STONE</strong></h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Diverse selections of Marble, Granite, Quartzite, Limestone,  &amp; Travertine.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2><strong>QUALITY SUPPLIER RELATIONSHIPS</strong></h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Access to our senior management, product specialists, logistics professionals, operations staff.</li>\r\n	<li>Supplier database contains over 100 worldwide.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2><strong>INTERNATIONALLY &amp; DOMESTICALLY SOURCED MATERIALS</strong></h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>New York Stone sources directly from quarries in Italy, Brazil, Turkey, Spain, and China. We also source domestically.</li>\r\n</ul>'),
